{"tid":1973490,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"慈善音樂會","createTime":"2020-04-15T08:27:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-17T04:16:38.000Z","uid":213437,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8cb0645c7b31dd4fa58512812461349b93af7414","tid":1973490,"uid":213437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T08:27:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C1WDf8O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC1WDf8O.jpg&h=25564d0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一場由香港一班有心嘅後生仔搞嘅一場音樂會，雖然而家環境因素唔好，但係佢地未去到一定做唔到嗰陣仍然會堅持完成自己嘅夢想。<br />\n而且今次活動仲會將全部收益捐贈比癌症病患者，同埋康復者，希望可以為佢地出少少力幫下佢地，希望大家可以支持下佢地🙏<br />\n<br />\n當然所有防疫措施都會做足，假如禁令延期先會阻止到佢地未能如期進行，感激🙏🙇🏼&zwj;♂️"},{"pid":"a4a123000008970e23a60eee313739bd4e8b5b31","tid":1973490,"uid":32353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T08:28:44.000Z","msg":"發大財"},{"pid":"9e123f37b67337ef23bd25503d91616f6c72412b","tid":1973490,"uid":356099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T08:44:58.000Z","msg":"點解係癌症"},{"pid":"a80b226df16039682f620d6da53d767d09d8733f","tid":1973490,"uid":257740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T08:46:26.000Z","msg":"G持"},{"pid":"30e450b8665f61a31a1e1d6707d4dc7f5465e471","tid":1973490,"uid":213437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e123f37b67337ef23bd25503d91616f6c72412b","tid":1973490,"uid":356099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T08:44:58.000Z","msg":"點解係癌症"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T10:11:46.000Z","msg":"因為癌症係香港嘅頭號殺手，每年平均都佔香港死亡人數嘅30%。而且我地都因為見證到其中一位親戚受癌症嘅煎熬，所以希望幫到香港每一位受癌症煎熬的朋友。雖然我地出嘅力可能只係好少，但係都想盡我地能力去幫到佢地。"},{"pid":"45d1924f29aff86c46e7ac33dc1bd408ab19b204","tid":1973490,"uid":178111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8cb0645c7b31dd4fa58512812461349b93af7414","tid":1973490,"uid":213437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T08:27:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i